  "If SMS messages aren't being sent:\n1. Verify API Key and Secret are correct (no extra spaces)\n2. Check that the From Number is a valid Vonage number you own\n3. Ensure recipient phone numbers include country code\n4. Check your Vonage account balance\n5. Review the Vonage Dashboard > SMS > Logs for delivery status": "",
  "If alerts aren't appearing:\n1. Verify OpenLP is running and the Remote plugin is active\n2. Ensure the Alerts plugin is enabled in OpenLP\n3. Check that the server URL is correct (try accessing it in a browser)\n4. Verify firewall settings allow connections on port 4316\n5. If using authentication, verify credentials are correct": "",
  "If messages are sent but not received:\n1. Check Vonage Dashboard > SMS > Logs for delivery status\n2. Verify the recipient number is correct and can receive SMS\n3. Some carriers may block messages from unknown numbers\n4. Check if the destination country has SMS restrictions": "",
  "If you receive invalid sender ID errors:\n1. Use a phone number you've purchased from Vonage\n2. Format the number in E.164 format (+14155551234)\n3. Note: Alphanumeric sender IDs may be restricted in some countries": "",
  "Important security notes:\n\n1. Always use HTTPS endpoints to encrypt backups in transit\n2. Use app-specific passwords when available (Nextcloud, ownCloud)\n3. Store backups in a folder with restricted access\n4. Periodically download and verify your backups are valid\n5. Consider encrypting sensitive backups with external tools before uploading": "",
